name: "Bubblepee & Optimisryhme"
description:
Tahun 2666 di markas Autocuan!

Bubblepee masih memiliki bank pertanyaan di dalam harddrivenya yang belum terjawab.
Mesin pencarian di internet pun sudah lama menyerah,
Hanya Optimisryhme seorang yang sabar meladeninya.

'kenapa kamu masih tahan menghadapi semua pertanyaan aku, Optimisryhme?' ujar Bubblepee.
'agar kamu tak jadi katak dalam gelembung sabun, Bubblepee!' jawab Optimisryhme.
'terima kasih' dibalasnya
'dengan senang hati' disambutnya

---

The year 2666 at the Autocuan headquarters!

Bubblepee still has a bank of unanswered questions on his hard drive.
Even search engines on the internet have long given up,
Only Optimisryhme is patient with him.

'why are you still enduring all my questions, Optimisryhme?' said Bubblepee.
'so you don't become katak dalam gelembung sabun*, Bubblepee!' replied Optimisryhme.
'thank you' he replied
'with pleasure' he greeted

*katak dalam gelembung sabun is a parable/proverb for someone who lacks insight, stupid, petty.
